cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.CC 

This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category cs.CL (Computation and Language) as it focuses on evaluating the compositionality of neural models of language. It could also belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) as it deals with neural networks and their ability to generalize. Additionally, it could be categorized under cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) as it focuses on neural models, and cs.CC (Computational Complexity) as it presents tests to evaluate the complexity of neural models.
